Jeremy Davies https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jeremy_Davies 0 Jeremy Davies (born Jeremy Boring; October 8, 1969) is an American film and television actor. He is known for portraying the Norse god Baldur in God of War, Corporal Upham in Saving Private Ryan, Daniel Faraday on the ABC series Lost and Dickie Bennett in the FX series Justified, for which he was twice nominated for a Primetime Emmy Award for Outstanding Guest Actor in a Drama Series, later winning in 2012.
